</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_164" id="80v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_164_r1l11"><expan cert="medium">L<ex>itte</ex>ra</expan> <expan>Erhart<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Vorſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_164_r1l12">Her Erhart Vörſter cʒü dem Newenhaws / Vmb die ſache die ſıch <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l13">vns vnd ew verlawffen het / von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> des Scheffels </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l14">das die von Eger cʒwıſchen vns berıchten / Nu begern vvir ew vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l15">den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> darauf keins argen cʒevvarten / vvir vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l16">vvolten ew das dann vor erberklıch ſchreıben / an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>offen<ex>en</ex></expan> brıef </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l17">ſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / daʒ vvir vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / vnd die <expan>darvnt<ex>er</ex></expan> verdacht ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l18">on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew vnd den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ſıcher ſein / <expan>ongeu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l20">in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> Vincencij / Anno 
<add><ab facs="#facs_164_r1l19">M<hi rend="sup">o</hi> cccc<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab></add> ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l21">Von ~ dem Rate</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l22">der Stat cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_164" id="80v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan cert="medium">L<ex>itte</ex>ra</expan>
<expan>Erhart<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Vorst<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Her Erhart Vörster czü dem Newenhaws, umb die sache, die sich
                                <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns und ew verlawffen het von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, des Scheffels, das die von Eger czwischen uns
                        berichten. Nu begern wir ew und den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> darauf
                        keins argen czewarten; wir und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, wir
                        wolten ew das dann vor erberklich schreiben an
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>offen<ex>en</ex></expan> brief so <expan>v<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, daz
                        wir und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und die
                            <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> verdacht sein on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew und den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> sicher
                        sein <expan>ongev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Vincencii anno <add>m<hi rend="sup">o</hi> cccc<hi rend="sup">o</hi></add> ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. <lb/>Von dem rate der stat czü
                        <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
